text: Lyudmila Osintseva also written as Ljudmila Osintseva (Russian: Людмила Осинцева, born 1938) is a Soviet former long track speed skater, who was active in the 1960s. Osintseva represented her nation at the World Allround Speed Skating Championships for Women in 1965, finishing 4th overall. She finished 3rd in the 1500m event. She also competed at other international competitions.
